comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-03T13:20:11.397Z",codex-audit,"Duplicate check evidence inherited from parent lineage: current open/in-progress lists were empty and related search results were closed prior audits,so this task tracks the new latest-state execution."
  "2026-05-03T13:25:10.236Z",codex-audit,"Dogfood evidence: temporary project at /tmp/pm-cli-dogfood-6L7tIo used sandboxed PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH and exercised init/create hierarchy/claim/update/append/comments/notes/learnings/files/docs/test add/test run/search/calendar/context/health/validate/close/release. All commands passed; close emitted expected warn-mode readiness warning for intentionally omitted resolution metadata."
  "2026-05-03T13:27:04.987Z",codex-audit,"Telemetry/Sentry analysis evidence: remote stack healthy, 24h telemetry count 2534, Sentry unresolved issues/logs empty, latest release has zero new groups. Seven-day telemetry shows top command volume in get/update/close/comments/search; slowest P95 commands are linked test, reindex, health, search; failure messages include local absolute paths in tracker-not-initialized errors, so telemetry redaction needs hardening for paths/PII even when capture_level=max."
  "2026-05-03T13:34:24.293Z",codex-audit,"Security hygiene evidence: current pm item documents were scanned for provided tokens, private host IPs, and private remote operation paths. Existing current item leaks in pm-ny6y, pm-cakn, pm-vhdc, and pm-r9ei were sanitized through pm mutations; current item scan now returns no matches. Append-only history streams still contain historical pre-redaction text; direct hand-editing would break replay/hash integrity, so this needs a dedicated audited pm redaction command."
  "2026-05-03T13:55:23.065Z",codex-audit,"Evidence: temp-project dogfood lifecycle passed; Sentry unresolved issues/logs clean; telemetry stack health and analytics reviewed; hybrid semantic search returned semantic matches; calendar week markdown rendered deadlines/events/recurrence; pm health --check-only ok including vectorization stale_items=0; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed 84 files/1178 tests with 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; pnpm security:scan passed; git diff --check passed; current pm item docs scan found no tracked sensitive host/token/password literals. Follow-ups: pm-xk39 for audited history-stream redaction, pm-xz1p for legacy linked-file validation hygiene."
